longBusinessSummary: ByggPartner Gruppen AB (publ) operates as a construction company in Sweden. The company engages in construction of community properties, housing, school, health, and other buildings; remodeling and construction of premises, homes, and offices; and wood construction. It also provides industry and houses, house east, and building services. The company was formerly known as ByggPartner i Dalarna Holding AB (publ) and changed its name to ByggPartner Gruppen AB (publ) in June 2022. ByggPartner Gruppen AB (publ) was founded in 1992 and is based in Borlänge, Sweden.
